snippet.title: One Night at Flumpty's 2 (Developer Commentary)
snippet.description:
Reupload!  Thanks to MoupSoup for sending me this video to post again, since I didn't have it anymore.  Brings back fond memories.

ONAF1 commentary: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B4cTJPZPdAA

MoupSoup's channel: http://bit.ly/1ZpmKGs

There's something I said towards the end of this video that I feel a little differently about now, basically about saying I don't want to make any more fan games and only work on original projects.  It's my passion to try making original things, but I think it's too limiting not to allow myself to make fan games.  Sometimes they're just fun to make and they lead to cool things.  That's why I made an Undertale fan game quite some time after this.
